<span id="Further_FEM_improvements"></span>
=== Ulteriori miglioramenti di FEM ===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The [[Image:FEM_ConstraintElectricChargeDensity.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ElectricChargeDensity|Electric Charge Density]] load now has a ''Concentrated'' checkbox in the ''Total Source'' mode to use concentrated instead of distributed load (making it also applicable to edges and vertices) with CalculiX. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/25237 Pull request #25237]
* The [[Image:FEM_ResultShow.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ResultShow|FEM results objects]] now support the animation of half cycles in addition to reversed full cycles. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/24129 Pull request #24129]
* The [[Image:FEM_ConstraintSectionPrint.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintSectionPrint|Section Print]] feature now supports 2D models and electric flux in electrostatic analyses. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/25081 Pull request #25081]
* The ''Neumann'' mode of the [[Image:FEM_ConstraintElectrostaticPotential.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintElectrostaticPotential|Electrostatic potential]] boundary condition can now be used to apply a magnetic flux density boundary condition. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/25897 Pull request #25897]
* In Z88 exports, materials and elements without references can now be used as default values for mesh elements that do not have explicit references. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29185 Pull request #29185]
* The ''Displace Mesh'' property was added to the refactored [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX solver]], making it possible to view true scale deformation of the mesh without having to use the Warp filter. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/27786 Pull request #27786]
* The ''addArrayFromFunction'' Python function was added, making it possible to create custom arrays based on the [[Image:FEM_PostPipelineFromResult.svg|24px]] [[FEM_PostPipelineFromResult|pipeline]] fields. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/26076 Pull request #26076]
* A context menu command to [[Image:FEM_MeshClearGroups.svg|24px]] [[FEM_MeshClearGroups|clear mesh groups]] was added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/27945 Pull request #27945]
* A log verbosity preference was added for [[Image:FEM_SolverElmer.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverElmer|Elmer]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28058 Pull request #28058]
* The ''None Field Color'' property was added to the [[Image:FEM_PostPipelineFromResult.svg|24px]] [[FEM_PostPipelineFromResult|results pipeline]] and filters to set the color when the displayed field is ''None'' (can be helpful e.g. when using the [[FEM_PostFilterGlyph|Glyph filter]]). [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28028 Pull request #28028]
* All solver commands are now always shown (even if a given solver is not installed) and are grouped in the toolbar as well as in the menu. The default icon in the toolbar depends on the default solver selected in the Preferences. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28144 Pull request #28144]
* Material assignments are now read from the [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX's]] {{FileName|.frd}} results files. They can't be accessed in FreeCAD yet, but they can be visualized in ParaView upon conversion to {{FileName|.vtm}} format. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/27847 Pull request #27847]
* The [[Image:FEM_MaterialMechanicalNonlinear.svg|24px]] [[FEM_MaterialMechanicalNonlinear|Non-linear mechanical material]] objects are now grouped under the [[Image:FEM_MaterialSolid.svg|24px]] [[FEM_MaterialSolid|Solid Material]] objects. The ''Geometrical Nonlinearity'' and ''Material Nonlinearity'' properties are now Boolean. The latter is enabled by default and only applied if any material in the analysis has a non-linear mechanical material object assigned to it. Otherwise, it is ignored. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/27862 Pull request #27862]
* The Z-refinement algorithm of [[Image:FEM_MeshNetgenFromShape.svg|24px]] [[FEM_MeshNetgenFromShape|Netgen]], allowing the creation of extruded meshes, now also supports shells. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28204 Pull request #28204]
* It is now possible to edit the input files for the meshers to add some custom commands for mesh generation, similar to what could already be done for the solvers. Some general preferences of the FEM Workbench were improved too. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/27942 Pull request #27942]
* The [[Image:FEM_ConstraintElectrostaticPotential.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintElectrostaticPotential|Electrostatic potential boundary condition]] is now named ''Electromagnetic boundary condition''. Some smaller renames were are done. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/27614 Pull request #27614]
* The [[Image:FEM_SolverZ88.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverZ88|Z88 solver]] was refactored. It can be used with both open-source versions of Z88 - Z88OS and Z88Adria. It supports several element types and basic features for linear analyses. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28944 Pull request #28944]
* The ''Iterations Control Parameter Field'' property was added to the [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX solver]] to allow adjusting the convergence criteria. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29227 Pull request #29227]
* The ''Beam Reduced Integration'' property of the [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX solver]] was replaced by the generalized ''Reduced Integration'' property that replaces standard solid, face (shell, 2D) and beam elements with their reduced integration counterparts. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29223 Pull request #29223]
* The refactored [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX solver]] is now used by default. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29220 Pull request #29220]
* The [[Image:FEM_ConstraintSectionPrint.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintSectionPrint|Section print]] feature can now be used with the [[Image:FEM_SolverZ88.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverZ88|Z88 solver]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29188 Pull request #29188]
* Materials now have the ''Material Name'' property, making it easier to identify the actual materials represented by the material objects in the Analysis container. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29609 Pull request #29609]
* Three new [[Image:FEM_Examples.svg|24px]] [[FEM_Examples|FEM examples]] were added for [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX]]: basic 1D fluid network, axisymmetric shaft and plane stress plate with a hole. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29697 Pull request #29697] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29711 Pull request #29711]
* Several [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX]] preference labels were changed for clarity, including geometrical nonlinearity, advanced solver controls, eigenmode count, and frequency bounds. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/30099 Pull request #30099]
* The Data and extractions widget no longer raises an exception if the pipeline is empty. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29739 Pull request #29739]
* [[Image:FEM_ConstraintDisplacement.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintDisplacement|Displacement boundary condition]] now correctly writes the rotations in radians for the [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX solver]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29689 Pull request #29689]
* Node indexing was improved for the [[Image:FEM_SolverZ88.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverZ88|Z88 solver]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29606 Pull request #29606]
* The ''Groups of Nodes'' property was removed to better handle groups in meshers. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29440 Pull request #29440]
* [[Image:FEM_ConstraintForce.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintForce|Force load]] now uses the global placement of the reference geometry for the force direction (for example, if the reference is inside a Part container). [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29513 Pull request #29513]
* The dependence of [[Image:FEM_Examples.svg|24px]] [[FEM_Examples|FEM examples]] on workbenches other than [[Part_Workbench|Part]] was removed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29488 Pull request #29488] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29438 Pull request #29438]
* For the [[FEM_MeshRegion|Mesh refinement]] command, the expected mesh property was changed to ''Mesh Refinement List''. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29554 Pull request #29554]
* The [[Image:FEM_SolverZ88.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverZ88|Z88 solver]] can now use different cross sections assigned to different truss elements. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29379 Pull request #29379]
* [[Image:FEM_ConstraintPressure.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintPressure|Pressure load]] now takes into account the shell thickness for plane stress models solved with the [[Image:FEM_SolverZ88.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverZ88|Z88 solver]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29377 Pull request #29377]
* The [[Image:FEM_SolverZ88.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverZ88|Z88 solver]] now uses materials and elements without references as default. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29185 Pull request #29185]
* The legacy SolverCalculiX object created with old FreeCAD versions is now updated to the new solver object. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29102 Pull request #29102]
* [[Image:FEM_ConstraintFixed.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ConstraintFixed|Fixed boundary condition]] now works properly (constrains only the available DOFs) for plane stress, plane strain, axisymmetric, membrane and truss elements. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28986 Pull request #28986]
* Some redundant log messages generated during the mesh element search stage for the [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|24px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX solver]] were removed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28049 Pull request #28049]
* The legacy ''get_ccx_version'' check searching for a very old version of [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX]] was removed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28194 Pull request #28194]
* Transparency was removed from equation icons to make their non-grayed-out state clearer. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28193 Pull request #28193]
* The [[Image:FEM_PostPipelineFromResult.svg|24px]] [[FEM_PostPipelineFromResult|results pipeline]] no longer crashes if its data is a mutiblock with a null block. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/28171 Pull request #28171]
* The [[Image:FEM_PostPipelineFromResult.svg|24px]] [[FEM_PostPipelineFromResult|pipeline]] frames now include time/frequency units for the refactored [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|CalculiX solver]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/27845 Pull request #27845]
* The [[Image:FEM_ClippingPlaneAdd.svg|24px]] [[FEM_ClippingPlaneAdd|clipping plane]] command can now be enabled in feature edit mode. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/25145 Pull request #25145]
* Mesh error handling was improved for the solvers, including proper error messages when there's no mesh or multiple meshes are present. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/29186 Pull request #29186]
</div>

